---
// Problem Section Component
---

<section id="why-moontax" class="z-20 w-full max-w-7xl mt-0 mx-auto pt-10 px-6 mb-24 md:mb-32 relative">
    <div class="group overflow-hidden bg-zinc-900 md:bg-gradient-to-br md:from-white/10 md:to-white/0 z-10 rounded-[2.5rem] mb-6 relative" style="position: relative; --border-gradient: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2), rgba(255, 255, 255, 0), rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1)); --border-radius-before: 2.5rem">
        <!-- Background Glow Effect -->
        <div class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 w-full h-1/2 bg-gradient-to-tr from-red-500/10 via-transparent to-transparent opacity-40 pointer-events-none"></div>
        
        <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-0">
            <!-- Text Content -->
            <div class="md:p-16 flex flex-col z-10 pt-8 pr-8 pb-8 pl-8 relative justify-center">
                <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-2xl bg-gradient-to-br from-white/10 to-white/5 border border-white/10 flex items-center justify-center mb-2">
                    <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="text-orange-500"><path d="M12 9v2"></path><path d="M12 17h.01"></path><path d="M10.29 3.86L1.82 18a2 2 0 0 0 1.71 3h16.94a2 2 0 0 0 1.71-3L13.71 3.86a2 2 0 0 0-3.42 0z"></path></svg>
                </div>
                
                <h2 class="leading-[1.1] md:text-4xl text-3xl font-semibold text-white tracking-tight font-manrope mt-6 mb-6">
                    Crypto Taxes are a Mess — And the IRS is Watching
                </h2>
                
                <div class="space-y-4 text-lg text-gray-400 font-sans leading-relaxed">
                    <p>Traditional accountants don't understand blockchain. Generic software fails on DeFi. Meanwhile, IRS enforcement is ramping up, and years of unreconciled trading activity are piling up.</p>
                    <ul class="space-y-2 text-base">
                        <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-red-400 mt-1">✕</span> Exchange data gaps & missing cost basis</li>
                        <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-red-400 mt-1">✕</span> DeFi complexity that software can't handle</li>
                        <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-red-400 mt-1">✕</span> Years of trading chaos across multiple wallets</li>
                        <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-red-400 mt-1">✕</span> Anxiety about potential IRS audits</li>
                    </ul>
                    <div class="pt-6">
                        <a href="/form" class="text-orange-400 hover:text-white font-medium inline-flex items-center gap-2 transition-colors">
                            See If You Qualify <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M5 12h14"></path><path d="m12 5 7 7-7 7"></path></svg>
                        </a>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Visual Content: Health Check UI -->
            <div class="relative min-h-[350px] md:min-h-[500px] bg-zinc-950/30 border-t md:border-t-0 md:border-l border-white/5 overflow-hidden font-geist flex items-center justify-center">
                <!-- Floating Status Card -->
                <div class="z-10 w-[90%] max-w-md py-8 md:p-6 relative">
                    <div class="rounded-2xl bg-zinc-900 border border-white/10 md:backdrop-blur-xl shadow-[0_20px_50px_-12px_rgba(0,0,0,0.8)] overflow-hidden">
                        <!-- Header -->
                        <div class="p-5 border-b border-white/5 flex items-center justify-between bg-white/[0.02]">
                            <div>
                                <h4 class="text-white font-normal font-sans text-sm tracking-wide">Data Health Status</h4>
                                <div class="flex items-center gap-2 mt-1">
                                    <span class="relative flex h-2 w-2 shrink-0">
                                      <span class="animate-ping absolute inline-flex h-full w-full rounded-full bg-red-400 opacity-75"></span>
                                      <span class="relative inline-flex rounded-full h-2 w-2 bg-red-500"></span>
                                    </span>
                                    <p class="text-red-500 text-xs font-normal tracking-wide">
                                        Audit Risk: High
                                    </p>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <!-- Content Rows -->
                        <div class="divide-y divide-white/5 text-sm font-sans">
                            <div class="p-3.5 flex items-center justify-between hover:bg-white/5 transition-colors">
                                <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
                                    <div class="w-8 h-8 rounded-lg bg-zinc-800 flex items-center justify-center text-zinc-400">
                                        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M21 12V7H5a2 2 0 0 1 0-4h14v4"></path><path d="M3 5v14a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h16v-5"></path><path d="M18 12a2 2 0 0 0 0 4h4v-4Z"></path></svg>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="flex flex-col">
                                        <span class="text-gray-200 font-normal">DeFi Wallet (MetaMask)</span>
                                        <span class="text-red-400 text-xs mt-0.5 font-normal">Missing cost basis - 452 txs</span>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <span class="text-red-400 font-mono text-[10px] border border-red-500/30 px-1.5 py-0.5 rounded">ERROR</span>
                            </div>
                            <div class="p-3.5 flex items-center justify-between hover:bg-white/5 transition-colors">
                                <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
                                    <div class="w-8 h-8 rounded-lg bg-zinc-800 flex items-center justify-center text-zinc-400">
                                        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"></circle><path d="M12 6v6l4 2"></path></svg>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="flex flex-col">
                                        <span class="text-gray-200 font-normal">Binance Account</span>
                                        <span class="text-orange-400 text-xs mt-0.5 font-normal">API Data Gap (2021-2023)</span>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <span class="text-orange-400 font-mono text-[10px] border border-orange-500/30 px-1.5 py-0.5 rounded">FIX</span>
                            </div>
                            <div class="p-3.5 flex items-center justify-between hover:bg-white/5 transition-colors">
                                <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
                                    <div class="w-8 h-8 rounded-lg bg-zinc-800 flex items-center justify-center text-zinc-400">
                                        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M12 22s8-4 8-10V5l-8-3-8 3v7c0 6 8 10 8 10z"></path></svg>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="flex flex-col">
                                        <span class="text-gray-200 font-normal">Phantom (Solana)</span>
                                        <span class="text-zinc-500 text-xs mt-0.5 font-normal">Unclassified Staking Rewards</span>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <span class="text-zinc-500 font-mono text-[10px] border border-zinc-500/30 px-1.5 py-0.5 rounded">CHECK</span>
                            </div>
                            <div class="p-3.5 flex items-center justify-between hover:bg-white/5 transition-colors">
                                <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
                                    <div class="w-8 h-8 rounded-lg bg-zinc-800 flex items-center justify-center text-zinc-400">
                                        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M20 7h-9"></path><path d="M14 17H5"></path><circle cx="17" cy="17" r="3"></circle><circle cx="7" cy="7" r="3"></circle></svg>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="flex flex-col">
                                        <span class="text-gray-200 font-normal">Ledger Hardware</span>
                                        <span class="text-red-400 text-xs mt-0.5 font-normal">Internal Transfer Loop</span>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <span class="text-red-400 font-mono text-[10px] border border-red-500/30 px-1.5 py-0.5 rounded">REPAIR</span>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Solution Section (Intro) -->
    <div class="text-center mb-12 mt-12 md:mt-24">
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-medium text-white font-manrope mb-4">We are Specialists, Not Generalists</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-400 max-w-2xl mx-auto">We decode complex blockchain transactions and accurately categorize every trade, transfer, and transaction for IRS compliance.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
        <!-- Card 1 -->
        <div class="group overflow-hidden flex flex-col hover:border-white/20 transition-colors duration-500 bg-zinc-900 md:bg-gradient-to-br md:from-white/5 md:to-white/0 rounded-[2rem] p-8 border border-white/10">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-zinc-800 flex items-center justify-center mb-6 text-white">
                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="22 12 18 12 15 21 9 3 6 12 2 12"></polyline></svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-3 font-manrope">Complex Data Reconciliation</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm leading-relaxed">We specialize in unraveling years of trading chaos, DeFi, staking, and high-volume transaction histories that break generic software.</p>
        </div>
        <!-- Card 2 -->
        <div class="group overflow-hidden flex flex-col hover:border-white/20 transition-colors duration-500 bg-zinc-900 md:bg-gradient-to-br md:from-white/5 md:to-white/0 rounded-[2rem] p-8 border border-white/10">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-zinc-800 flex items-center justify-center mb-6 text-white">
                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M14 2H6a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v16a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h12a2 2 0 0 0 2-2V8z"></path><polyline points="14 2 14 8 20 8"></polyline><line x1="16" y1="13" x2="8" y2="13"></line><line x1="16" y1="17" x2="8" y2="17"></line><polyline points="10 9 9 9 8 9"></polyline></svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-3 font-manrope">Platform Integration</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm leading-relaxed">We work within your preferred crypto tax platform (CoinTracker, Koinly, etc.) to ensure your data is clean where you need it.</p>
        </div>
        <!-- Card 3 -->
        <div class="group overflow-hidden flex flex-col hover:border-white/20 transition-colors duration-500 bg-zinc-900 md:bg-gradient-to-br md:from-white/5 md:to-white/0 rounded-[2rem] p-8 border border-white/10">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-zinc-800 flex items-center justify-center mb-6 text-white">
                 <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M12 22s8-4 8-10V5l-8-3-8 3v7c0 6 8 10 8 10z"></path><path d="m9 12 2 2 4-4"></path></svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-3 font-manrope">Full Ecosystem Support</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm leading-relaxed">Backed by CPAI automation, Olson & Partners Law for legal opinions, and Securus Advisors for tax strategy and filing.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
